# Hardware

## Controller

- Adafruit HUZZAH32 ESP32 Feather

---

## Display

SSD1306 OLED (128×32)

| Signal | ESP32 GPIO |
|---------|------------|
| SDA | GPIO 23 |
| SCL | GPIO 22 |
| VCC | 3.3 V |
| GND | GND |

---

## LEDs

Each LED should be connected through a **220 Ω resistor**.

| LED | GPIO |
|------|------|
| Green | GPIO 13 |
| Red | GPIO 12 |

Configuration:

```
GPIO → 220 Ω resistor → LED anode
LED cathode → GND
```

---

## Relay

| Signal | GPIO |
|---------|------|
| Relay | GPIO 26 |

Operation:

- Active HIGH
- 500 ms pulse

